# Phase 3 + Offline Cache — Implementation Plan

## Goal
Implement the Phase 3 standout features from the SachCheck roadmap, plus the **Offline Cache for Recent Verifications** feature. This transforms SachDrishti from a basic fact-checker into a polished, feature-rich app.

## Scope

| # | Feature | Effort | Status |
|---|---------|--------|--------|
| 1 | **Offline Cache for Recent Verifications** | Low | History already stores `matchedArticlesJson` in Hive — need to surface articles in `HistoryDetailScreen` |
| 2 | **Share Sheet Integration** | Medium | Register Android intent filter for images; route shared images to `/processing` |
| 3 | **Credibility Score Dashboard** | ✅ Done | Already built into `ProfileScreen` with Firestore stats |
| 4 | **Export Verification Report** | Low | `ReportGenerator` exists but isn't wired to UI — wire it + use text-based share as fallback |
| 5 | **Multi-Language OCR** | Low | Add Hindi/Bengali/Tamil script recognizers to `OcrService` |

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Credibility Score Dashboard** is already fully implemented in `ProfileScreen` (score circle, stats grid, Firestore integration). No work needed. The plan below covers the remaining 5 items.

