## Proposed Changes

### 1. Offline Cache — Surface Matched Articles in History Detail

The data layer is already complete: `HistoryItem.matchedArticlesJson` stores serialized articles in Hive. The gap is that `HistoryDetailScreen` doesn't decode and display them.

#### [MODIFY] [history_detail_screen.dart](file:///c:/Users/devic/AndroidStudioProjects/sachcheck/lib/screens/history/history_detail_screen.dart)

- Import `dart:convert` and `verification_result.dart` (for `Article.fromCacheJson`)
- Add a `_cachedArticles` getter that decodes `matchedArticlesJson`
- Add a "Matched Sources" section (identical design to `ResultScreen._ArticleCard`) between the score bar and search resources
- Show an "Available offline" badge when articles are present
- If no cached articles, show "No cached articles" message

---

### 2. Share Sheet Integration — Android Intent Filter

#### [MODIFY] [AndroidManifest.xml](file:///c:/Users/devic/AndroidStudioProjects/sachcheck/android/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml)

Add a second `<intent-filter>` to `MainActivity` to receive shared images:
```xml
<intent-filter>
    <action android:name="android.intent.action.SEND"/>
    <category android:name="android.intent.category.DEFAULT"/>
    <data android:mimeType="image/*"/>
</intent-filter>
```

#### [NEW] [share_receiver_service.dart](file:///c:/Users/devic/AndroidStudioProjects/sachcheck/lib/services/share_receiver_service.dart)

- Uses `MethodChannel` to receive the shared image path from the Android activity
- Provides a stream/callback that the app listens to on startup

#### [MODIFY] [MainActivity.kt](file:///c:/Users/devic/AndroidStudioProjects/sachcheck/android/app/src/main/kotlin/com/example/sachcheck/MainActivity.kt)

- Override `getInitialIntent` / handle `intent.action == Intent.ACTION_SEND`
- Extract the image URI and pass it to Flutter via a `MethodChannel`

#### [MODIFY] [main.dart](file:///c:/Users/devic/AndroidStudioProjects/sachcheck/lib/main.dart)

- On app start, check for a shared image via `ShareReceiverService`
- If found, navigate to `/processing` with the shared image path

#### [MODIFY] [router.dart](file:///c:/Users/devic/AndroidStudioProjects/sachcheck/lib/core/router.dart)

- Add a `pendingShareImage` provider that routes can check after auth

